title: Iced Earth - The PLagues EP
description:
North American metallers ICED EARTH will make a special 12-inch vinyl EP available on their upcoming European tour with VOLBEAT, which kicks off October 11 in Milan, Italy and wraps December 1 in Copenhagen, Denmark.

The details are as follows:

* A 12" 180g vinyl EP 
* Limited, hand-numbered edition (1000 units only) 
* Blood-red vinyl 
* Heavy-duty cardboard sleeve with matte print

Featuring the world premiere of the following songs:

* Plagues Of Babylon
* If I Could See You
* Peacemaker


Read more at http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/iced-earth-to-release-limited-edition-the-plagues-vinyl-ep/#VV7HIA1OQFIbbyeh.99
